This map is my new map create by Darkapple and Alien team [FR]

To install it :
1) Go to C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\SteamApps\common\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\maps
2) Extract Zip 
3) place Namemap.bsp in folder maps
4) Play 

Have fun !!!

This map content More secret ;) And Flash secret
